takeholders. Fluency in English, both written and spoken; proficiency in German is a plus. Benefits Equity (every Berlin employee gets real shares) BVG transport subsidy Breakfast and lunch in the office, daily Language courses Urban Sports Club 5 days a week in the Berlin office Join as a Venture Manager in Berlin. Earn €110k + equity while growing a generational company. Find Jobs in Germany on Arbeitnow",
